<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. فَأَفْرَادُنَا ظَنُّوَا النَّجَا فِي التَّنَسُكِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَغَالِبُنَا مِنْهَاجُهُم في التَّسَلُّكِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَمِلَّةِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ مِنْ خَيْرِ مَسْلَكِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَلَيْسَ لها مِنْ سَالِكِ مُتَمَسِّكِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>بِدِين النَّبِي الأَبْطَحِي بن هَاشِمِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَلَسْنَا نَرَى مَا حَلَّ فِي الديِّنِ وَامّحَتْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>بِهِ الْمِلَّةِ السَّمْحَاءِ إِحْدَى الْقَوَاصِمِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>عَسَى تَوْبَةٌ تَمْحُو ذُنُوبًا لِمُرْتَجِي<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>عَسَى نَظْرَةٌ تَسْلُكْ بِنَا خَيْرَ مَنْهَجِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>عَسَى وَعَسَى مِنْ نَفْحَةٍ عَلَّهَا تَجِي<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَنَأْسَى عَلَى التَّقْصِيرِ مِنَّا وَنَلْتَجِي<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>إِلى اللهِ فِي مَحْوِ الذُّنُوبِ الْعَظَائِمِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فَكُلُّ الْوَرَى فِي كَثْرَةِ الْمَالِ نَافَسَتْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَرَانَتْ ذُنُوبٌ فِي الْقُلُوبِ وَقَدْ رَسَتْ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَفِي النَّهْيِ عَنْ كُلِّ الْمَعَاصِي تَنَاعَسَتْ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فَنَشْكُوا إِلى اللهِ الْقُلوبَ التِي قَسَتْ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَراَنَ عَلَيْهَا كَسْبُ تِلْكَ الْمَآثِمِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>نُرَاعِي أَخَا الدُّنْيَا فَذَاكَ هُوَ الأَخُ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَلَوْ كَانَ فِي كُلِّ الْمَعَاصِي مُلَطَّخُ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>أَلَسْنَا بَأَوْضَارِ الْخَطَا نتَضَمَّخُ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>أَلَسْنَا إِذَا مَا جَاءَنَا مُتَضَمِّخُ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>